../../website/src/metadata/skill-base-rivetkit.md:24:Use the inspector HTTP API to examine running actors. These endpoints are accessible through the gateway at `/gateway/{actor_id}/inspector/*`. Key endpoints:
../../website/src/metadata/skill-base-rivetkit.md:26:- `GET /inspector/summary` - full actor snapshot (state, connections, RPCs, queue)
../../website/src/metadata/skill-base-rivetkit.md:27:- `GET /inspector/state` / `PATCH /inspector/state` - read/write actor state
../../website/src/metadata/skill-base-rivetkit.md:28:- `GET /inspector/connections` - active connections
../../website/src/metadata/skill-base-rivetkit.md:29:- `GET /inspector/rpcs` - available actions
../../website/src/metadata/skill-base-rivetkit.md:30:- `POST /inspector/action/{name}` - execute an action with `{"args": [...]}`
../../website/src/metadata/skill-base-rivetkit.md:31:- `POST /inspector/database/execute` - run SQL with `{"sql": "...", "args": [...]}` or `{"sql": "...", "properties": {...}}` for reads or mutations
../../website/src/metadata/skill-base-rivetkit.md:32:- `GET /inspector/queue?limit=50` - queue status
../../website/src/metadata/skill-base-rivetkit.md:33:- `GET /inspector/traces?startMs=0&endMs=...&limit=1000` - trace spans (OTLP JSON)
../../website/src/metadata/skill-base-rivetkit.md:34:- `GET /inspector/workflow-history` - workflow history and status as JSON (`nameRegistry`, `entries`, `entryMetadata`)
../../website/src/metadata/skill-base-rivetkit.md:35:- `POST /inspector/workflow/replay` - replay a workflow from a specific step or from the beginning
../../website/src/metadata/skill-base-rivetkit.md:36:- `GET /inspector/database/schema` - SQLite tables and views exposed by `c.db`
../../website/src/metadata/skill-base-rivetkit.md:37:- `GET /inspector/database/rows?table=...&limit=100&offset=0` - paged SQLite rows for a table or view
../../website/src/metadata/skill-base-rivetkit.md:38:- `POST /inspector/workflow/replay` - replay a workflow from a specific step or from the beginning
